$ GRUB
abbr: Grand Unified Bootloader
wp:GNU_GRUB

GRUB can not only load Linux but other Operating Systems as well.


Arguably the most flexible →development/boot-loader for →Linux/index. Other Linux boot loader are → Linux/booting/SYSLINUX and → Linux/booting/LILO.

